{"tid":109774,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 10 Cloud 畫面曝光   挑戰 Chrome OS","createTime":"2017-02-06T07:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T15:15:43.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef8a0ff96c988924bdfa60541f1fb5198d66dae4","tid":109774,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:51:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/02/06/windows-10-cloud-challenge-chrome-os/software/win10/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F02%2F06%2Fwindows-10-cloud-challenge-chrome-os%2Fsoftware%2Fwin10%2F&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfpwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=9e310a15\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/02/06/windows-10-cloud-challenge-chrome-os/software/win10/</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然在香港市場仍未流行，Chrome OS 和 Chromebook 在美國已經擁有不少用戶，原因之一是 Chromebook 售價普遍非常便宜，加上 Google 去年宣佈 Chromebook 可運行 Android Apps，預計今年會有更多用戶考慮使用。Microsoft 亦意識到 Chrome OS 來勢洶洶，準備了 Windows 10 Cloud 系統迎戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/06/154910_6824f3d5da7d0bed2e2a06caf1a55f99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F06%2F154910_6824f3d5da7d0bed2e2a06caf1a55f99.jpg&h=113d82a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWindows 10 Cloud 和 Windows 10 在使用上十分類似，但最大分別是並非所有 Windows 軟件都能夠正常運作。Windows 10 Cloud 只支援在 Windows Store 內的 Universal Windows Platform Apps，這對於 Chromebook 的目標顧客，教育市場的用家十分重要，能夠保持大量軟件可以在 Windows Store 下載，但同時減少學生或兒童安裝未經准許的軟件或遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，亦減低惡意軟件在系統中出現的機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n這個特殊的系統暫時還未知道正式上市的日期，預計會在今年首季的 Windows 10 Creators Update 中出現。"},{"pid":"432442fed74d17426bcf8367ba95bfa6e0b952f7","tid":109774,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:09:26.000Z","msg":"Windows RT ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0641bc56c7cdb4a882eb448a4da3ff541b1caa","tid":109774,"uid":29862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:11:36.000Z","msg":"我仲用緊win xp"},{"pid":"f0d7a526c20148f31c2732456c4459807185c418","tid":109774,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:35:59.000Z","msg":"據外媒報道，微軟正在為Windows 10開發新的Cloud SKU，以對抗谷歌的Chrome OS。據悉，Windows 10 Cloud將會是輕量版的Windows操作系統，很可能專為ARM架構的處理器而開發。<br />\n<br />\n近日，網友@adguard在推特上上傳了Windows 10 Cloud的ISO文件，感興趣的用戶可以下載安裝。<br />\n<a href=\"https://cloud.mail.ru/public/Jybd/6WwDzndqD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloud.mail.ru%2Fpublic%2FJybd%2F6WwDzndqD&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfpwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=64c4eacb\" target=\"_blank\">https://cloud.mail.ru/public/Jybd/6WwDzndqD</a><br />\n<br />\n根據早前的報道，Windows 10 Cloud只能夠運行從Windows Store裡下載安裝的Universal Windows Platform（通用Windows平台）程式。當筆者嘗試在Windows Cloud 10中安裝微軟的Visual Studio Code（Win32程式）時，會出現「該應用程式並不是為此Windows版本設計」的警告。再次證明，該版本的SKU只允許用戶運行Windows Store中的程式。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s314.siliconimg.com/kb/content_images/2017/02/06/1265298/1486385671_836.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs314.siliconimg.com%2Fkb%2Fcontent_images%2F2017%2F02%2F06%2F1265298%2F1486385671_836.jpg&h=bf757b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1265298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hksilicon.com%2Farticles%2F1265298&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfpwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=b7e873d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1265298</a>"},{"pid":"ab503d08a13e6ebdba33461c86ccf0789047db16","tid":109774,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}